! SCORM Debugger: TASBot-Inspired QA Automation
''Summary:'' Vue.js wrapper with fake SCORM API providing emulator save-state functionality for eLearning QA: save course state at any point, restore instantly, edit SCORM values directly, jump to any section. Reduced testing cycles from hours to minutes for gated content. Addresses a gap in commercial SCORM tools — reproducible debug states and session state inspection are not first-class features in SCORM Cloud or SCORM Engine.
