! Investigation Summary

Created a Vue.js SCORM debugging tool inspired by TASBot/speedrunning save states. Reduced QA testing cycles from hours to minutes by enabling instant state capture and restore across gated eLearning courses. The approach that Rustici Engine’s testing tools would later address commercially.

